    "name": "Silque",
    "epitet": "Adherent of Mila",
    "display": "Silque: Adherent of Mila",
    "description": "A cleric from Novis who sought out Alm in order to deliver a certain item to him. Has a sweet but serious personality. Appears in Fire Emblem Echoes: Shadows of Valentia.",
    "artist": "lack",
    "voiceActorEN": "Bonnie Gordon",
    "voiceActorJP": "いのくちゆか",
    "dialogue": [
        {
            "text": "I am Silque. I have come to save the people of this world through Mother Mila's teachings.",
            "context": "joined"
        },
        {
            "text": "I have traveled to many places, but I must say, the beauty of this world is truly a sight to behold.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "I fought alongside Sir Alm to protect Zofia from Rigel.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "War can leave scars no one can see... If I can ease your burden by listening, please, do not hesitate to call on me.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "I was going to invite my friend Faye for tea... Would you care to join us?",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "I was just praying to Mother Mila, that she might grant the people of this world her divine protection.",
            "context": "castle"
        },
        {
            "text": "How have you been? I ask on the behalf of <Friend Name>.",
            "context": "friend"
        },
        {
            "text": "I can hardly believe such strength is available to me... It must be due to your guidance, surely.",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "I shall strive ever forward...at whatever pace I can manage.",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "I'm so sorry. I will redevote myself to my training...",
            "context": "level"
        },
        {
            "text": "With this, I hope to be of even more use to your cause.",
            "context": "growth"
        },
        {
            "text": "You and I are but travelers passing through this country, it seems. Before long, it will be time to move on... I want those I meet to remember my face as one wearing a smile, so I try to hide any sadness I might feel. But with you...it's different. I want you to see me as I truly am. And hope you feel the same for me. No matter what lies in your heart, you will find only acceptance from me—and empathy for your pain. When we depart from this world, the hurt we share will make the good memories that much brighter.",
            "context": "maxed"
        }
    ],
